    <pre>Take a look at this page: <a href="https://openhatch.org/+projects/blender">https://openhatch.org/+projects/blender</a>

Here are some problems:

* The "projects" navigation link above the word "Blender" is practically invisible

* Yet it takes up vertical space

This simple patch compresses the "Projects" link to be on the same line as the
link to "Blender".</pre>
